* primary hypotheses - higher risk of depression/anixety if lower ability for social activity 

logistic DEP SOCIALbin
logistic DEP ageGRP sex dwell urbanrural smoke alcohol houseCAT income multimorb depFU1 moodFU1 anxFU1 SOCIALbin

logistic ANX SOCIALbin
logistic ANX ageGRP sex dwell urbanrural smoke alcohol houseCAT income multimorb depFU1 moodFU1 anxFU1 SOCIALbin

logistic DEP INTOUCHbin
logistic DEP ageGRP sex dwell urbanrural smoke alcohol houseCAT income multimorb depFU1 moodFU1 anxFU1 INTOUCHbin

logistic ANX INTOUCHbin
logistic ANX ageGRP sex dwell urbanrural smoke alcohol houseCAT income multimorb depFU1 moodFU1 anxFU1 INTOUCHbin

* primary hypotheses - higher risk of depression/anixety if lower ability for physical activity 

logistic DEP PHYSbin
logistic DEP ageGRP sex dwell urbanrural smoke alcohol houseCAT income multimorb depFU1 moodFU1 anxFU1 PHYSbin
logistic ANX PHYSbin
logistic ANX ageGRP sex dwell urbanrural smoke alcohol houseCAT income multimorb depFU1 moodFU1 anxFU1 PHYSbin

* secondary hypotheses - greater risk of depression/anxiety if higher preCOVID social activity and lower COVID social activity 

* dichotomous * 
by socialDICHFU1, sort :logistic DEP SOCIALbin
by socialDICHFU1, sort :logistic DEP ageGRP sex dwell urbanrural smoke alcohol houseCAT income multimorb depFU1 moodFU1 anxFU1 SOCIALbin

by socialDICHFU1, sort :logistic ANX SOCIALbin
by socialDICHFU1, sort :logistic ANX ageGRP sex dwell urbanrural smoke alcohol houseCAT income multimorb depFU1 moodFU1 anxFU1 SOCIALbin

by socialDICHFU1, sort : logistic DEP INTOUCHbin
by socialDICHFU1, sort : logistic DEP ageGRP sex dwell urbanrural smoke alcohol houseCAT income multimorb depFU1 moodFU1 anxFU1 SOCIALbin

by socialDICHFU1, sort : logistic ANX INTOUCHbin
by socialDICHFU1, sort : logistic ANX ageGRP sex dwell urbanrural smoke alcohol houseCAT income multimorb depFU1 moodFU1 anxFU1 INTOUCHbin

* quintiles *

by socialQUINTFU1, sort :logistic DEP SOCIALbin
by socialQUINTFU1, sort :logistic DEP ageGRP sex dwell urbanrural smoke alcohol houseCAT income multimorb depFU1 moodFU1 anxFU1 SOCIALbin

by socialQUINTFU1, sort :logistic ANX SOCIALbin

by socialQUINTFU1, sort :logistic ANX ageGRP sex dwell urbanrural smoke alcohol houseCAT income multimorb depFU1 moodFU1 anxFU1 SOCIALbin

by socialQUINTFU1, sort : logistic DEP INTOUCHbin

by socialQUINTFU1, sort : logistic DEP ageGRP sex dwell urbanrural smoke alcohol houseCAT income multimorb depFU1 moodFU1 anxFU1 SOCIALbin

by socialQUINTFU1, sort : logistic ANX INTOUCHbin
by socialQUINTFU1, sort : logistic ANX ageGRP sex dwell urbanrural smoke alcohol houseCAT income multimorb depFU1 moodFU1 anxFU1 INTOUCHbin


* secondary hypotheses - greater risk of depression/anxiety if higher preCOVID physical and lower COVID physical 

* high vs low 
by paseHL, sort :logistic DEP PHYSbin
by paseHL, sort :logistic DEP ageGRP sex dwell urbanrural smoke alcohol houseCAT income multimorb depFU1 moodFU1 anxFU1 PHYSbin
by paseHL, sort :logistic ANX PHYSbin
by paseHL, sort :logistic ANX ageGRP sex dwell urbanrural smoke alcohol houseCAT income multimorb depFU1 moodFU1 anxFU1 PHYSbin


* adjusting for physical activity

logistic DEP ageGRP sex dwell urbanrural smoke alcohol houseCAT income multimorb depFU1 moodFU1 anxFU1 paseHL PHYSbin

logistic ANX ageGRP sex dwell urbanrural smoke alcohol houseCAT income multimorb depFU1 moodFU1 anxFU1 paseHL PHYSbin


